Java Based Basic Network Simulator
Created using Java and Java Swings
Step 1 - Create nodes by choosing the node tab and left mouse click on drawing platform.
Step 2 - Draw Links between each node where first clicked node is the source.
Step 3 - Choose source node as TCP and destination as TCPSink and create a transfer link between them.
Step 4 - Create a FTP point at source node.
Step 5 - Choose a simulation algorithm and compare each.
